title: Introducing 'Market Matchup': AMD Versus NVDA | Making Money With Matt McCall

media:group.media:title: Introducing 'Market Matchup': AMD Versus NVDA | Making Money With Matt McCall
media:group.media:description:
Stocks are attempting to rally from a two-year low. Yet investors are becoming more nervous about the future of the market. Does this rally have legs, though? Could it possibly last? Well, in this episode of Making Money With Matt McCall, Matt takes a look under the hood of the market. He highlights several sentiment indicators that are at levels we've rarely seen before.

Then, Matt introduces a new segment on the show called Market Matchup. He takes two companies, pits them against each other, and breaks them down. He's starting off the segment with two giants in the semiconductor sector: Advanced Micro Devices (AMD) versus Nvidia (NVDA). You won't want to miss who will win this battle of technology heavyweights.
